{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban workplace or private pensions being considered in divorce settlements",
        "additional_details": "We think allowing pensions to be considered in divorce settlements can lead to unfairness, for example where one party has opted out of their workplace pension.",
        "background": "People may be relying on their pension to retire comfortably and without leading to poverty, and then the unforeseen could happen and they've lost 50% of their pension, which doesn't allow for a comfortable retirement.",
